External knowledge:
- 'most-supported' refers to the suggestions with the highest 'support_length' (i.e., the number of supporters); 
- 'top three' refers to the three suggestions with the highest 'support_length';
- 'Harlem' is a neighborhood in New York City.

sql:
SELECT submission_date, status
FROM suggestions
ORDER BY submission_date;
